# VCS / metadata
.git
.gitignore
.turbo
**/*.md
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md

# Dependency installs (regenerated inside image)
**/node_modules

# Build outputs (regenerated inside image)
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.astro
**/coverage
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc

# Secrets: NEVER bake into image (compose injects via env_file at runtime)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!.env.example

# Docker artifacts (not needed inside images)
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

# Test sources (not shipped)
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.js
**/*.test.js
chatbot/tests

# IDE / OS
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/.npm
**/.pnpm-debug.log*
